text: Staff was efficient and courteous. Good variety of pastries and savoury sandwiches even on a late Saturday evening. I got the mini chocolate twists as takeaway. Tasted quite burnt with little chocolate flavours. The pastry though was nice, crisp and buttery even after leaving in the fridge.

2nd time here as wait for my medicine from TTSH.
The coffee beanâ€™s caffeine is strong than others, single shot can cause heart beat faster. Nothing wrong, depends on your choice.

Paris Baguette at Novena Square 2 Mall offers a wide selection of breakfast options, making it an excellent choice to start your day. The service is impressively fast, ensuring you get your meal quickly, even during busy hours. Additionally, the prices are reasonable, providing great value for the quality and variety offered. Overall, it's a fantastic spot for a quick and satisfying breakfast.

There is an ongoing promotion until 22 April 2024 at this new outlet. 2 tarts for $4.90. Any 5 breads for $10 applicable only for those lower priced items.

There are some seats for dining-in.

Breads look yummy. A little pricey than regular bakeries.

Newly opened Paris Baguette! Quite a wide selection of bread, and a decent amount of seats. They serve tea and brunch menus here too! I bought my favourite cream cheese pastry roll and enjoyed it in-store~
